**Service Intensity Levels**
| Level | Description | Examples |
|-------|-------------|----------|
| Minimal | Few hours, periodic | Volunteer visitor, informal |
| Moderate | Regular schedule | Adult day, weekly in-home |
| Intensive | Extended duration | Overnight, residential stays |
